# File Naming and Organization Conventions

## Section Files (sections/)

### Naming Patterns
- **Standard sections**: `section-name.liquid` (e.g., `header.liquid`, `footer.liquid`)
- **Namespaced sections**: `prefix--section-name.liquid` (e.g., `nine15--slider.liquid`)
- **Template-specific sections**: `template--section-name.liquid`

### Section Categories
- **Navigation**: `navigation.liquid`, `side-navigation.liquid`
- **Product-related**: `main-product.liquid`, `featured-collection.liquid`, `main-collection-product-grid.liquid`
- **Content**: `main-page.liquid`, `contact-form.liquid`, `main-article.liquid`
- **Cart**: `main-cart-items.liquid`, `cart-hear-about-us.liquid`
- **Custom**: `paver-banner.liquid`, `custom-fields-products.liquid`

## Snippet Files (snippets/)

### Naming Patterns
- **Master components**: `master--component-name.liquid` (e.g., `master--slider.liquid`)
- **Reusable snippets**: `snippet--name.liquid` (e.g., `snippet--video.liquid`)
- **Custom fields**: `custom_fields.entity.field_name.liquid`
- **Product-specific**: `product-field-name.liquid`
- **Shopify integrations**: `shopify--service--component.liquid`

### Snippet Categories
- **Head elements**: `head--meta-tags.liquid`, `head--scripts.liquid`, `head--styles.liquid`
- **Product components**: `card-product.liquid`, `buy-buttons.liquid`, `product-media-gallery.liquid`
- **Navigation**: `navigation-content.liquid`, `simple-menu.liquid`
- **Custom fields**: `custom_fields.articles.*`, `custom_fields.collections.*`
- **Third-party integrations**: `klaviyo-*.liquid`, `revy-bundle-script.liquid`

## Template Files (templates/)

### JSON Templates
- **Standard templates**: `template-name.json` (e.g., `index.json`, `product.json`)
- **Template variants**: `template.template-suffix.json`
  - `product.bookshelf.json`
  - `page.contact.json`
  - `article.field-notes-article.json`

### Liquid Templates
- **Customer templates**: `customers/template-name.liquid`
- **Special templates**: `gift_card.liquid`, `password.json`

## Asset Files (assets/)

### CSS/SCSS Files
- **Main stylesheets**: `theme.css`, `base.css`
- **Component styles**: `component-name.css`
- **Page-specific**: `page-name.css`

### JavaScript Files
- **Core scripts**: `theme.js`, `common.js`
- **Component scripts**: `component-name.js`
- **Third-party**: `vendor-library-name.js`

### Image Files
- **Icons**: `icon-name.svg`, `icon-name.png`
- **Backgrounds**: `bg-name.jpg`, `pattern-name.png`
- **Product placeholders**: `product-placeholder.jpg`

## Locale Files (locales/)

### Translation Files
- **Base language**: `en.default.json`, `en.default.schema.json`
- **Other languages**: `language-code.json`, `language-code.schema.json`
- **Regional variants**: `language-REGION.json` (e.g., `pt-BR.json`, `zh-CN.json`)

## Configuration Files (config/)

### Theme Configuration
- **Settings**: `settings_data.json`, `settings_schema.json`
- **Markets**: `markets.json`

## File Organization Principles

### Directory Structure
```
sections/          # Theme sections
├── header.liquid
├── footer.liquid
├── nine15--slider.liquid
└── custom-fields-products.liquid

snippets/          # Reusable components
├── master--slider.liquid
├── snippet--video.liquid
├── head--scripts.liquid
└── custom_fields.articles.*.liquid

templates/         # Page templates
├── index.json
├── product.json
├── product.bookshelf.json
└── customers/
    └── account.json
```

### Naming Best Practices

1. **Use descriptive names**: `main-collection-product-grid.liquid` vs `grid.liquid`
2. **Consistent prefixes**: `master--` for complex components, `snippet--` for simple snippets
3. **Hyphen separation**: Use hyphens for multi-word names
4. **Avoid abbreviations**: `navigation.liquid` vs `nav.liquid`
5. **Template suffixes**: Use dots for template variants (`product.bookshelf.json`)

### Special File Types

#### Custom Fields
- **Articles**: `custom_fields.articles.field_name.liquid`
- **Products**: `custom_fields.products.field_name.liquid`
- **Collections**: `custom_fields.collections.field_name.liquid`

#### Shopify Integrations
- **Discovery**: `shopify--discovery--service.liquid`
- **Apps**: `app-name--component.liquid`

#### Third-party Integrations
- **Klaviyo**: `klaviyo-form.liquid`, `klaviyo-sold-out.liquid`
- **Reviews**: `revy-bundle-script.liquid`

### File Extensions
- **Liquid templates**: `.liquid`
- **JSON templates**: `.json`
- **Stylesheets**: `.css`, `.scss`
- **JavaScript**: `.js`
- **Images**: `.jpg`, `.png`, `.svg`, `.webp`
